Package: Paleopollen
Type: Package
Title: Provides useful tools for paleoecology and pollen analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Robin", "von Allmen", , "robinvonallmen@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides paleo ecologists with the necessairy tool to create more modern pollen stratigraphies. It includes methods that can be used to compare multiple stratigraphies, compares samples through Principal Component analysis (PCA) and Cluster analysis (CA).
